$$r\equiv \begin{cases}a^{(p+3)/8}\pmod{p}&\text{if }d\equiv 1\pmod{p}\\
2a(4a)^{(p-5)/8}\pmod{p}&\text{if }d\equiv p-1\pmod{p}\end{cases}$$

